data.text:
Marianna Municipal Airport

& Marianna Airport Commerce Park

The Marianna Airport Commerce Park offers a unique combination of a first-class, renovated, historic, friendly, municipal airport and a Commerce Park that offers move-in ready buildings and shovel-ready land. If you need a place to refuel, or you need to leave your plane here during your cave diving trip, or you’ve dream of locating your business next to an airport, you found the right place.
